"""
Enhance the script from Challenge 8. Define a new string variable with the value "Programming" and combine it with the previous string.
Print the concatenated string. Additionally, use string formatting to create a message that includes both strings.
This task evaluates your ability to concatenate strings and use string formatting in Python.
"""

string = "Python"
string2 = "Programming"

print(f"The concatenation of words '{string}' and '{string2}' is '{string+string2}'\n"
      f"I'm studying and {string2} in {string}")
